Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.tree.avltree

Class AbstractAvlTreeGeneric<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.tree.avltree.AbstractAvlTreeGeneric<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsGeneric<T>, TreeOpsGeneric<T>
public abstract class AbstractAvlTreeGeneric<T> extends Object implements TreeOpsGeneric<T>

Title: AbstractAvlTreeGeneric

Description:

Template for the structure of a generic AVL tree implementation Note that an AVL tree is a self-balancing tree which checks the height of subtrees to ensure that the left and right subtrees don't have a height greater than one
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
